categories: Default Category/No web item
name: Tagger HeavyDuty Pistol Long
description:
Avery Dennison Taggers are the industry standard! Avery Dennison invented high productivity tagging and the tools continue to set industry standards. Swifttach is available in Standard and fine taggers. Pistol grip taggers and scissor grip are available. Fine tools use fine needles and fine fasteners and are used for tagging anything t-shirt thickness or finer. Both the micro tagger and the system 1000 tagger use specialized fasteners.

All brands of standard fasteners are interchangeable with other taggers as all brands of fine fasteners may be used with any fine tagging gun. Needles may not be interchangeable.
